title: Trump 2020 Campaign Kickoff, Fed Chair Powell Future, Trade
itunes:title: Trump 2020 Campaign Kickoff, Fed Chair Powell Future, Trade
description:
Guests include: Kevin Walling, Democratic Strategist at HG Creative Media and Matt Gorman, Vice President at Targeted Victory & Former NRCC Communications Director.

Marc Lotter, Trump 2020 Campaign Strategic Communications Director called in live from Orlando ahead of President Trump’s formal kick off speech for his 2020 re-election bid.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
